+```ts
+// event-store.ts: implements EventStore with append(event) and listByRun(runId), ordered by sequence.
+// session-store.ts: implements SessionStore with create/get/getByRunId/update.
+// artifact-store.ts: implements ArtifactStore with create/get/update plus listByRun(runId).
+```
